flowchart LR
    %% Artifact Data Flow — Requirement to Proof to Memory

    AN([analysis.md]) -->|Findings| SP([spec.md])
    SP -->|Decompose| PL([plan.md / tasks.md])

    PL -->|Execute| CODE[(Source Code)]

    CODE -->|Validate| RV([review.md])
    RV -->|Pass| SX([session-extracts.md])
    SX -->|Triage / promote| MEM[(memories/repo/*)]
    RV -->|Consolidate| HO([handoff.md])

    %% Feedback loops
    RV -.->|Drift detected| SP
    RV -.->|Code fix loop| PL
    MEM -.->|Smarter next feature| AN

    classDef default fill:#f7f7f5,stroke:#e0e0e0,color:#111
    classDef code fill:#ebf5ed,stroke:#c3e0c5,color:#2d7d32
    classDef review fill:#fcf3f3,stroke:#f2c4c4,color:#c62828
    classDef mem fill:#eef2ff,stroke:#c7d2fe,color:#3730a3
    classDef handoff fill:#f0f4f8,stroke:#d9e2ec,color:#334e68

    class CODE code
    class RV review
    class MEM,SX mem
    class HO handoff
